<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SEC Learning Portal</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --paper:#FBF7EF; --card:#FFFFFF; --ink:#221A0F; --muted:#8A7A63; --faint:#B3A488;
  --border:#EAE0CC; --border-strong:#DCCFB2;
  --amber:#B45309; --amber-bright:#F59E0B; --amber-soft:#FDF3E3; --amber-line:#F1DDB8;
  --green:#1D7A46; --green-soft:#E9F5EE; --red:#B3372F; --red-soft:#FBEDEB;
  --serif:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif; --sans:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
  --mono:ui-monospace,'SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;
  --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(60,42,10,.06),0 6px 20px rgba(60,42,10,.07);
  --radius:14px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html,body{height:100%}
body{font-family:var(--sans);background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
button{font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer}
input,textarea,select{font-family:inherit;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink)}
a{color:var(--amber)}
::selection{background:var(--amber-line)}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em}
.hidden{display:none!important}

/* ---------- brand ---------- */
.brand-mark{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:9px;object-fit:cover;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(20,20,60,.35);flex:none}
.brand-mark.lg{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:12px}

/* ---------- buttons / inputs ---------- */
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;justify-content:center;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:11px 20px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;transition:transform .08s ease,box-shadow .12s ease,background .12s}
.btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
.btn-primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D97706,#B45309);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(180,83,9,.3)}
.btn-primary:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(180,83,9,.4)}
.btn-primary:disabled{opacity:.45;cursor:not-allowed;box-shadow:none}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--muted);border:1px solid var(--border-strong)}
.btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--ink);border-color:var(--faint)}
.btn-danger{background:var(--red);color:#fff}
.btn-sm{padding:6px 12px;font-size:13px;border-radius:8px}
.field{margin-bottom:14px}
.field label{display:block;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:6px}
.field input,.field textarea,.field select{width:100%;padding:11px 13px;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:10px;background:#fff;transition:border-color .12s,box-shadow .12s}
.field input:focus,.field textarea:focus,.field select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--amber-bright);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(245,158,11,.18)}
.err{background:var(--red-soft);color:var(--red);border:1px solid #EBC6C1;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 13px;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:14px}
.ok-note{background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green);border:1px solid #C4E3D0;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 13px;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:14px}

/* ---------- login ---------- */
.login-wrap{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;background:
  radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 80% -10%,rgba(245,158,11,.10),transparent 60%),
  radial-gradient(900px 500px at -10% 110%,rgba(180,83,9,.08),transparent 55%),var(--paper)}
.login-card{width:100%;max-width:420px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);padding:40px 36px}
.login-head{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px}
.login-head h1{font-size:27px;margin:16px 0 6px}
.tagline{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;color:var(--muted);font-size:15.5px}
.login-foot{text-align:center;margin-top:20px;font-size:13.5px}
.login-foot button{background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:13.5px;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}
.login-foot button:hover{color:var(--amber)}

/* ---------- topbar / shell ---------- */
.topbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:40;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px 24px;background:rgba(251,247,239,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.topbar .title{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:17px}
.topbar .spacer{flex:1}
.pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--amber-soft);border:1px solid var(--amber-line);color:#92400E;border-radius:999px;padding:5px 13px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600}
.shell{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px 80px}

/* ---------- dashboard ---------- */
.greeting{font-size:30px;margin-bottom:4px}
.role-badge{display:inline-block;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:7px;padding:4px 10px;color:var(--muted);margin:8px 0 22px}
.overall{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:18px 22px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:28px}
.overall .lbl{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:8px}
.pbar{height:8px;background:var(--border);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden}
.pbar>div{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#F59E0B,#B45309);border-radius:99px;transition:width .5s ease}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
@media(max-width:760px){.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.shell{padding:24px 16px 60px}}
.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
.card .row{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:flex-start}
.card h3{font-size:19px;line-height:1.3}
.card .desc{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;margin-top:6px}
.card .meta{font-size:13px;color:var(--faint);display:flex;gap:14px}
.chip{display:inline-block;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;border-radius:999px;padding:3px 11px}
.chip.grey{background:#F1ECE0;color:var(--muted)}
.chip.amber{background:var(--amber-soft);color:#92400E;border:1px solid var(--amber-line)}
.chip.green{background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green)}
.ring{transform:rotate(-90deg)}
.ring .bg{stroke:var(--border)}
.ring .fg{stroke:url(#ringGrad);stroke-linecap:round;transition:stroke-dashoffset .6s ease}
.ring-wrap{position:relative;flex:none}
.ring-num{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--amber)}

/* ---------- subject view ---------- */
.subj-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:270px 1fr;gap:28px;align-items:start}
@media(max-width:860px){.subj-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.sidebar{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);position:sticky;top:76px}
.sec-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;width:100%;text-align:left;background:none;border:none;border-radius:9px;padding:10px 11px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.35}
.sec-item:hover:not(:disabled){background:var(--amber-soft)}
.sec-item.active{background:var(--amber-soft);font-weight:600}
.sec-item:disabled{color:var(--faint);cursor:not-allowed}
.sec-dot{flex:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;border:2px solid var(--border-strong);color:var(--muted);background:#fff}
.sec-dot.progress{background:var(--amber-bright);border-color:var(--amber-bright);color:#fff}
.sec-dot.done{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:#fff}
.subj-main{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);min-height:420px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.back-link{background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:18px;padding:4px 0}
.back-link:hover{color:var(--amber)}

/* ---------- reader ---------- */
.reader-head{padding:26px 30px 0}
.eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:8px}
.reader-head h1{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:4px}
.reader-body{padding:20px 30px 26px;overflow-y:auto;max-height:56vh}
.clause-block{border-left:3px solid var(--amber-bright);background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(245,158,11,.06),transparent 60%);border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:16px}
.clause-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber);margin-bottom:6px;letter-spacing:.02em}
.clause-block p{white-space:pre-line;font-size:14.5px}
.timer-banner{margin:0 30px 24px;background:var(--amber-soft);border:1px solid var(--amber-line);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:14px;color:#92400E}
.timer-banner strong{font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}

/* ---------- quiz ---------- */
.quiz-wrap{padding:30px}
.q-progress{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.09em;margin-bottom:10px}
.q-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;line-height:1.45;margin-bottom:22px}
.opt{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;width:100%;text-align:left;background:#fff;border:1.5px solid var(--border-strong);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.45;transition:border-color .1s,background .1s}
.opt:hover{border-color:var(--amber-bright)}
.opt.sel{border-color:var(--amber);background:var(--amber-soft)}
.opt .letter{flex:none;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--amber-soft);border:1px solid var(--amber-line);color:#92400E;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.opt.sel .letter{background:var(--amber);border-color:var(--amber);color:#fff}
.opt.right{border-color:var(--green);background:var(--green-soft)}
.opt.right .letter{background:var(--green);border-color:var(--green);color:#fff}
.opt.wrong{border-color:var(--red);background:var(--red-soft)}
.opt.wrong .letter{background:var(--red);border-color:var(--red);color:#fff}
.explain{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--red);background:var(--red-soft);border-radius:9px;padding:10px 14px;margin:-4px 0 14px}
.quiz-foot{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:8px}

/* ---------- complete states ---------- */
.celebrate{padding:56px 30px;text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.celebrate .big{font-size:52px;line-height:1}
.celebrate h2{font-size:26px}
.celebrate .stats{display:flex;gap:26px;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;margin:6px 0 8px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.celebrate .stats b{color:var(--ink);font-size:18px;display:block;font-family:var(--serif)}

/* ---------- admin ---------- */
.tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding-bottom:0}
.tab{background:none;border:none;border-bottom:2.5px solid transparent;padding:9px 16px;font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted)}
.tab.active{color:var(--amber);border-bottom-color:var(--amber)}
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-bottom:26px}
.stat{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:18px 20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.stat .n{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:30px;font-weight:600}
.stat .l{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;font-weight:600;margin-top:2px}
table.members{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow);font-size:13.5px}
table.members th{text-align:left;font-size:11.5px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--muted);padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:#FDFAF3}
table.members td{padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:middle}
table.members tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
table.members tbody tr{cursor:pointer}
table.members tbody tr:hover{background:var(--amber-soft)}
.minibar{width:90px;height:6px;background:var(--border);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px}
.minibar>div{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#F59E0B,#B45309)}
.del-x{background:none;border:none;color:var(--faint);font-size:16px;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px}
.del-x:hover{color:var(--red);background:var(--red-soft)}
.panel-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(34,26,15,.35);z-index:50}
.detail-panel{position:fixed;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;width:min(560px,94vw);background:var(--card);z-index:51;box-shadow:-12px 0 40px rgba(34,26,15,.18);overflow-y:auto;padding:28px;animation:slidein .22s ease}
@keyframes slidein{from{transform:translateX(40px);opacity:0}to{transform:none;opacity:1}}
.detail-panel h2{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:2px}
.detail-panel .sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:13.5px;margin-bottom:18px}
table.breakdown{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:20px}
table.breakdown th{text-align:left;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--muted);padding:7px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
table.breakdown td{padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
details.attempts{margin-bottom:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;background:#FDFAF3}
details.attempts summary{cursor:pointer;font-weight:600}
.att{margin:10px 0 4px;padding-left:8px;border-left:2px solid var(--border-strong)}
.att .hd{font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px}
.att .qr{color:var(--muted);margin-left:8px}
.att .qr .yes{color:var(--green)} .att .qr .no{color:var(--red)}
.flag{color:#B45309;font-weight:700}
.gen-q{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:14px;background:#fff}
.gen-q .qt{font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px}
.gen-q .go{display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:flex-start;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13.5px;margin-bottom:5px;border:1px solid transparent}
.gen-q .go.correct{background:var(--green-soft);border-color:#C4E3D0;font-weight:600}
.gen-q .ex{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px;font-style:italic}
.gen-q .acts{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:10px}
.warn-banner{background:#FFF7E6;border:1px solid var(--amber-line);color:#92400E;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:18px}
.reg-row{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:14px}
.reg-row .em{flex:1;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px}
.settings-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:22px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:20px;max-width:620px}
.settings-card h3{font-size:17px;margin-bottom:14px}
.spin{display:inline-block;width:15px;height:15px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4);border-top-color:#fff;border-radius:50%;animation:sp .7s linear infinite;vertical-align:-3px}
@keyframes sp{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*{animation:none!important;transition:none!important}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute"><defs>
<linearGradient id="ringGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
<stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F59E0B"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#B45309"/>
</linearGradient></defs></svg>

<div id="app"></div>

<script>
/* ═══════════════ CONFIG ═══════════════ */
const SHEETS_API_URL = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbwk2AyWHM3PsOMKIffZ_UJdj2DnaA_gid6v2LFV99_q0RkxlPCxrJ6E7wVdN0GFiAzScQ/exec";
const LOGO_SRC = "sunway_entrepreneurs_club_logo.jpeg";

let sessionToken = sessionStorage.getItem("sec_token") || null;
let currentUser  = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem("sec_user") || "null");

async function api(body) {
  if (sessionToken) body.token = sessionToken;
  const res = await fetch(SHEETS_API_URL, {
    method: "POST",
    headers: { "Content-Type": "text/plain;charset=utf-8" },
    body: JSON.stringify(body)
  });
  return res.json();
}
const esc = s => String(s ?? "").replace(/&/g,"&amp;").replace(/</g,"&lt;").replace(/>/g,"&gt;").replace(/"/g,"&quot;");
const $ = sel => document.querySelector(sel);
const app = document.getElementById("app");

/* ═══════════════ SUBJECT DATA — SEC CHARTER 2026–2027 ═══════════════ */
const SUBJECTS = [
  {
    id: "charter",
    title: "SEC Club Charter 2026–2027",
    description: "Foundational governance document. All committee members must complete this before taking on any responsibilities.",
    estimatedMinutes: 45,
    sections: [
      { id: "definitions", title: "Part 0 — Definitions & Role Codes", clauses: [
        { label:"Committee member", text:"Any individual holding a named role within the Club's committee structure, including ExCo, departmental officers, and Control & Support Officers." },
        { label:"President (R-01)", text:"The ExCo member designated as President for the term, serving as the Club's official representative and final escalation authority. The President permanently holds the Brand & Content portfolio (R-02) directly, in the same manner the Treasurer Function (R-09) is permanently embedded under the VP, Events (R-05) — see clause 4.4.1." },
        { label:"Vice President (R-02–R-05)", text:"One of four portfolio leads forming the Executive Committee, each owning a defined domain. Current titles and portfolios are listed in Appendix A1. The Brand & Content portfolio (R-02) is permanently held by the President rather than independently assigned each term; R-03 through R-05 are independently assigned." },
        { label:"Secretary (R-06)", text:"A standalone Control & Support Officer supporting all VP portfolios. Not embedded in any single VP domain. Operates under the strategic direction of R-01." },
        { label:"Vice Secretary (R-07)", text:"The officer assisting the Secretary (R-06) in meeting minutes, documentation systems, records management, governance tracking, and administrative follow-up." },
        { label:"Treasurer (R-09)", text:"The officer holding the Treasurer Function, embedded operationally under R-05. Responsible for budget control, financial records, and all treasurer-related functions." },
        { label:"Club Auditor (R-08)", text:"An independent standalone Control & Support Officer responsible for reviewing account security, AI usage, financial documentation, reconciliation work, task tracking, and governance compliance. Reports to R-01 and ExCo. Retains full independence on audit findings." },
        { label:"AWI Officer (R-11)", text:"AI & Web Innovation Officer. A standalone Control & Support Officer responsible for Club technology infrastructure, digital tools, web presence, and AI systems. Operates under the strategic direction of R-01 and provides operational support across all VP portfolios." },
        { label:"Role Code (R-##)", text:"A permanent identifier assigned to each committee role. Codes do not change when role titles are renamed. See Appendix A1 for current title mapping." },
        { label:"Unauthorised Person", text:"Any individual not formally permitted to access specific Club information, documents, discussions, records, decisions, or communication channels under this Charter." },
        { label:"Tier 1 Member", text:"A Community Pool Participant who has joined Sunway Nexus by SEC at no cost." },
        { label:"Tier 2 Member", text:"A registered paid Active SEC Member, as defined in clause 2.2." }
      ]},
      { id: "club-info", title: "Part 1 — Vision, Mission & Objectives", clauses: [
        { label:"1.2 Vision", text:"To be Sunway University's leading entrepreneurship ecosystem — a self-sustaining platform of digital authority, owned community, and proven execution that produces operators, not just members, and that strengthens with every committee handover rather than resetting to zero." },
        { label:"1.3 Mission", text:"To build a community of aspiring entrepreneurs and innovators, fostering real-world skills, professional connections, and opportunities beyond campus to help members turn their ideas into reality and become future business leaders." },
        { label:"1.4 Objectives", text:"Develop Operators, Not Just Members: Equip students with practical skills, creative thinking, and entrepreneurial values through curated training, mentorship, and hands-on projects.\n\nBuild Digital Authority: Establish SEC's social presence as a credibility platform that reaches strangers and sponsors, not just existing members — the entry point to the SEC flywheel.\n\nBuild Owned Community Infrastructure: Grow Sunway Nexus by SEC into a warm, owned audience that reduces SEC's dependence on cold outreach for attendance and recruitment.\n\nRun an Activation Platform: Deliver events that function as a proof layer — documented, repeatable, content-producing — converting digital authority into physical credibility rather than one-off activity.\n\nBuild Institutional Assets: Maintain the D-01–D-07 document system and Notion infrastructure so each incoming committee inherits a working system, not a blank slate.\n\nProvide Real-World Pathways: Create internship, training, and working-experience pathways for members within Sunway Education Group and industry partners." },
        { label:"1.5 Powers", text:"The Club has the same powers as an individual, subject to this Charter. The Club may exercise those powers and use its income and assets only for the purposes set out in its Vision, Mission, and Objectives, and in accordance with University, Student LIFE, and SUSC/SCC requirements." }
      ]},
      { id: "membership", title: "Part 2 — Membership Tiers & Data Handling", clauses: [
        { label:"Tier 1 Membership — Community Pool (Free)", text:"Tier 1 is free and open to all students enrolled at Sunway University or Sunway College, students from formally recognised partner institutions, alumni of Sunway Education Group, and external partners engaged through Sunway Nexus by SEC. Participants join via the Sunway Nexus by SEC WhatsApp Community Platform." },
        { label:"Tier 1 — Not Entitled To", text:"Voting rights in any SEC decision or meeting. Priority registration for limited-seat events. Discounted or free entry to ticketed events. Year-end certificate of membership. Direct personal connection to SEC's sponsor network as an individual. Eligibility to join the SEC committee or hold a leadership position." },
        { label:"Tier 2 Membership — Active SEC Members (RM10)", text:"A membership fee of RM10 is required. Payment must be made via bank transfer or QR code. All payments must be receipted and recorded by R-09.\n\nParticipation in Club events and activities is voluntary. Tier 2 membership status shall not be contingent on a minimum attendance or participation requirement, and a member shall not be marked inactive or have their membership affected solely on the basis of non-attendance. The Club does not compel attendance: where an event delivers genuine value, members attend by choice. SEC practises mature community-building and does not enforce presence at activities that do not serve the member." },
